Smoking cessation treatment for individuals with comorbid diabetes and serious 
mental illness in an integrated health care delivery system.

Hwong AR(1), Schmittdiel J(2), Schillinger D(3), Newcomer JW(4), Essock S(5), 
Zhu Z(2), Dyer W(2), Young-Wolff KC(6), Mangurian C(7).

Author information:
(1)University of California, San Francisco, Weill Institute of Neurosciences, 
Department of Psychiatry, USA. Electronic address: Alison.Hwong@ucsf.edu.
(2)Kaiser Permanente Northern California Division of Research, Oakland, CA, USA.
(3)UCSF Center for Vulnerable Populations at Zuckerberg San Francisco General 
Hospital, USA; UCSF Division of General Internal Medicine at Zuckerberg San 
Francisco General Hospital, USA.
(4)Thriving Mind South Florida, Miami, FL, USA; Washington University School of 
