Exploring the transcriptomic network of multi-ligand scavenger receptor 
Stabilin-1- and Stabilin-2-deficient liver sinusoidal endothelial cells.

Olsavszky V(1), Sticht C(2), Schmid CD(3), Winkler M(3), Wohlfeil SA(4), 
